rComments: I only completed 1 of 8 Journals, 1 of 8 Discussion Boards, All homework and tests - and I got an A, she was very lenient, plus I answered a lot of bonus credit essay questions on tests.

It is so easy. You get 2 chances to do the online hw assignments, she averages the 2 scores... but after you take it once you get all the answers! You don't have to go to class at all, only when there is a movie or for a test. Take it with a friend! The tests are straight from the homework! SO EASY
Loved the class.  Study the homeworks for the test, and make sure you do the online assignments.  Also try and take it with a friend.
Fairly easy class, Hail was very knowledgeable about the topics. The test questions came straight from the online homeworks. She made everything simple, not a tricky teacher.
